  <section id="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Faithful Haven isn’t just a community, it’s a space for healing, hope, and faith. 
      We welcome anyone going through mental health struggles, no matter your age, gender, or background. 
      Whether you’re in a dark place or simply seeking peace, you belong here.
      <br><br>
      This is a space for people who feel deeply, dream big, and sometimes feel lost or broken. 
      At Faithful Haven, we believe healing comes not just from professional help, but also from shared stories, 
      real connection, and growing in faith,together.
      <br><br>
      Let’s create a place where we lift each other up, see the world through new eyes, and remind each other 
      that even in the middle of pain, hope and healing are possible.
    </p>
  </section>

