          this space, a place where people can come together, be honest, and help each other heal through shared 
          experiences and faith.
          <br><br>
          I’ve always dreamed of starting this community before turning 18,not because I have all the answers, 
          but because I believe in the power of connection, love, and vulnerability. Faithful Haven isn’t launched yet, 
          but it’s in the making,and that’s okay. What matters is the heart behind it.
          <br><br>
